Source: FacebookThe categories of the awards are as follows:1. Banking and Financial Services2. Energy and Environment3. Entrepreneur4. ICT5. Manufacturing and FMCG6. Media and Marketing7. Mining and Minerals8. Service: Public and Private9. Professional Services10. Tourism, Retail and Hospitality11. Transport, Logistics and SecurityCandidates must be under 40 years of age. Nominations close 30 April and the awards ceremony will take place on 20 October in Sandton.For more information, click here.